metadata.name: [#2 Burned] Ready for Takeoff
metadata.description:
The card was broken by the conductor and marked with the word "Burned". A mysterious glow can be seen inside and the number 2 is visible. Its former power remains uncertain, but its value does not appear to have diminished.
